 Galvatron landed infront of Prime. He transformed into robot mode. This was 
no time for games. This was the ultimate battle. He sent a video feed to the 
fight to every liveing bot on the planet. They would be able to see the fight 
in thier own optics if they wished. Storm clouds flooded the sky. "Now isnt 
this fiiting."

--part1_50.123df629.27d512fb_boundary
